# quantum-quackery/_redirects
# Cloudflare Pages redirect rules.

# API calls from the landing page proxy to Render
# (alternative to calling Render directly — avoids mixed content
#  and keeps the API URL consistent if you ever move hosts)
/api/*  https://atelier-api.quantumquackery.com/:splat  200

# Redirect bare domain to www (or remove if you prefer bare)
# http://quantumquackery.org/*  https://www.quantumquackery.org/:splat  301
